er/IP telephony; and cloud solutions, such as virtual desktops on cloud, cloud monitoring and management, AWS services, and silver cloud, as well as public, private, and hybrid cloud. The company was formerly known as Silver Touch Computers Limited and changed its name to Silver Touch Technologies Limited in October 2004. Silver Touch Technologies Limited was founded in 1992 and is headquartered in Ahmedabad, India."}}